[Name] dvdauthor
[Summary] A simple set of tools to help with authoring a DVD.
[License] GNU General Public License (GPL)
[Description] dvdauthor is a simple set of tools to help with authoring a 
DVD. It will eventually be able to create menus, buttons,  
and chapters, etc, but for now it takes an MPEG stream 
and writes it to DVD.
[Homepage] http://dvdauthor.sourceforge.net
